                            <comment id="118141" author="isaac" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2015 21:34:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Then we&apos;d make it clear in the documentation. Maybe I missed something but I couldn&apos;t find any doc on the fact that multiple OSTs per pool is not supported.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="118077" author="bzzz" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2015 17:12:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we decided long ago do not put few OSTs into a single ZFS pool. for the number of reasons: space management, ro capability, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
